%N A397322 Expansion of e.g.f. (1/x) * Series_Reversion( x*(1 + x*log(1-x^4)) ).
%F A397322 E.g.f. A(x) satisfies A(x) = 1 - x * A(x)^2 * log(1 - (x * A(x))^4).
%F A397322 a(n) = (1/(n+1)) * Sum_{k=0..floor(n/4)} (2*n-4*k)! * |Stirling1(k,n-4*k)|/k!.
%o A397322 (PARI) a(n) = sum(k=0, n\4, (2*n-4*k)!*abs(stirling(k, n-4*k, 1))/k!)/(n+1);
